data.meta_description: See Babyface Live on tour Babyface at the Mystic Lake Showroom Prior Lake, MN. Oct 4.  Buy tickets online now or find out more with Minneapolis Theater
data.text:
An evening with Kenneth "Babyface" Edmonds

Enjoy an evening set to the soothing and smooth sounds of Kenneth "Babyface" Edmonds who will be lighting up stages across the country this year. Joined by special guests, don't miss this night for lovers, friends, and fans of some of R&B's greatest songs.

Throughout his glittering career, Babyface has received eleven Grammy Awards, been ranked number 20 on NME's 50 Of The Greatest Producers Ever list and been given an acclaimed star on the Hollywood Walk of Fame. Some of his most loved hits include "Tender Lover," "For The Cool In You" and "Grown & Sexy."
